{"Title": "The BiPo-3 detector for the measurement of ultra low natural radioactivities of thin materials", "Year": 2017, "Source": "J. Instrum.", "Volume": "12", "Issue": 6, "Art.No": null, "PageStart": null, "PageEnd": null, "CitedBy": 12, "DOI": "10.1088/1748-0221/12/06/P06002", "Link": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=85023179351&origin=inward", "Abstract": "\u00a9 2017 IOP Publishing Ltd and Sissa Medialab srl.The BiPo-3 detector, running at the Canfranc Underground Laboratory (Laboratorio Subterr&apos;aneo de Canfranc, LSC, Spain) since 2013, is a low-radioactivity detector dedicated to measuring ultra low natural radionuclide contaminations of 208Tl (232Th chain) and 214Bi (238U chain) in thin materials. The total sensitive surface area of the detector is 3.6 m2. The detector has been developed to measure the radiopurity of the selenium double \u03b2-decay source foils of the SuperNEMO experiment. In this paper the design and performance of the detector, and results of the background measurements in 208Tl and 214Bi, are presented, and the validation of the BiPo-3 measurement with a calibrated aluminium foil is discussed. Results of the 208Tl and 214Bi activity measurements of the first enriched 82Se foils of the double \u03b2-decay SuperNEMO experiment are reported. The sensitivity of the BiPo-3 detector for the measurement of the SuperNEMO 82Se foils is (208Tl) <2 \u03bcBq/kg (90% C.L.) and (214Bi) <140 \u03bcBq/kg (90% C.L.) after 6 months of measurement.", "AuthorKeywords": ["Double-beta decay detectors", "Radiation monitoring", "Spectrometers"], "IndexKeywords": ["Activity measurements", "Double beta decay", "Low-radioactivity", "Natural radioactivity", "Natural radionuclides", "Radiation monitoring", "Thin materials", "Underground laboratory"], "DocumentType": "Journal", "PublicationStage": null, "OpenAccess": 0, "EID": "2-s2.0-85023179351", "SubjectAreas": [["Mathematical Physics", "MATH", "2610"], ["Instrumentation", "PHYS", "3105"]], "AuthorData": {"7007134563": {"Name": "Barabash A.S.", "AuthorID": "7007134563", "AffiliationID": "60020943, 60018710", "AffiliationName": "NRC, Kurchatov Institute, ITEP"}, "7103125863": {"Name": "Konovalov S.I.", "AuthorID": "7103125863", "AffiliationID": "60020943, 60018710", "AffiliationName": "NRC, Kurchatov Institute, ITEP"}, "6701765598": {"Name": "Umatov V.I.", "AuthorID": "6701765598", "AffiliationID": "60020943, 60018710", "AffiliationName": "NRC, Kurchatov Institute, ITEP"}, "34876378400": {"Name": "Basharina-Freshville A.", "AuthorID": "34876378400", "AffiliationID": "60003771", "AffiliationName": "University of Manchester"}, "26658869400": {"Name": "Cascella M.", "AuthorID": "26658869400", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College London"}, "57190006147": {"Name": "Chopra A.", "AuthorID": "57190006147", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College London"}, "56043566400": {"Name": "Eurin G.", "AuthorID": "56043566400", "AffiliationID": "60073296, 60106017, 60000383", "AffiliationName": "LAL, Universit\u00e9 Paris-Sud, CNRS/IN2P3, Universit\u00e9 Paris-Saclay"}, "57193402688": {"Name": "Flack R.", "AuthorID": "57193402688", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College London"}, "55196156000": {"Name": "Kauer M.", "AuthorID": "55196156000", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College London"}, "57206737862": {"Name": "Liu X.R.", "AuthorID": "57206737862", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College London"}, "48261270800": {"Name": "Mott J.", "AuthorID": "48261270800", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College London"}, "57196557811": {"Name": "Richards B.", "AuthorID": "57196557811", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College London"}, "15081116100": {"Name": "Saakyan R.", "AuthorID": "15081116100", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "University College Londo